        {
            "title": "〈熱門股〉自動化族群回春了！上銀、大銀3月營收靚 股價周漲2成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">台股自動化族群本周表現亮眼，上銀 (2049-TW)4/17 收在 291 元，創 1 年多新高，獲外資連 3 買，本周累計漲幅 20.25%；同集團的大銀微系統 (4576-TW)4/17 收在 196 元，本周累計漲幅 18.79%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上銀 3 月營收 23.57 億元，年增 17.4%，創下 29 個月以來的高點。隨著全球製造業 PMI 回升，上銀 2026 全年營收有望挑戰雙位數成長。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-3dfc58d5-3161-3643-99d3-8e8b73cca272-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大銀微系統 3 月營收亮麗，達 3.21 億元，月增 25.96%、年增達 49.5%，創下近 4 年來新高，顯示精密運動控制元件的需求正隨著半導體設備復甦而快速反彈。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">上銀攜手大銀日前聯合參展「2026 台北電子生產製造設備展」，大銀推出新型奈米級定位平台，整合多維度模組與驅控一體化控制系統，以因應前端市場的高階應用需求；並結合上銀 PLP 自動化次系統，為客戶提供完整且高效的整合解決方案。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">隨著 AI 技術與發展，市場對高階傳動元件如滾珠螺桿、線性滑軌與精密定位系統需求大增，其中，大銀微米及奈米級定位系統在手訂單能見度高達 4-6 個月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">法人指出，經歷長達一年多的產業去庫存，工具機與自動化組件的庫存水位已降至健康水準，中國及東南亞市場的拉貨動能明顯回升。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"上銀日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/SdY7oMYMXJ4alqSlKqLxBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/5618ce3fe70b78e0374060c2d0e6ecf5\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">上銀日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"大銀微系統日 K 線圖\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"500\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/R5S_Iu4eVMU0qwdoquZ6yg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTgyOA--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/fecf24e0b7f201e06fcf5cc80bae7d52\" width=\"580\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:580px\">大銀微系統日 K 線圖</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"> </p><p class=\"mb-module-gap read-more-vendor break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span>更多鉅亨報導</span><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"〈焦點股〉半導體、機器人雙題材發威 大銀微系統強勢攻漲停創歷史新高\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:〈焦點股〉半導體、機器人雙題材發威 大銀微系統強勢攻漲停創歷史新高;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6418325?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">〈焦點股〉半導體、機器人雙題材發威 大銀微系統強勢攻漲停創歷史新高</a><br/>•<a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"戰事掀原物料漲價潮！上銀部分產品調漲7-15% 訂單能見度4個月\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:戰事掀原物料漲價潮！上銀部分產品調漲7-15% 訂單能見度4個月;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6396846?utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_medium=RSS&amp;utm_campaign=relate\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">戰事掀原物料漲價潮！上銀部分產品調漲7-15% 訂單能見度4個月</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%86%B1%E9%96%80%E8%82%A1-%E8%87%AA%E5%8B%95%E5%8C%96%E6%97%8F%E7%BE%A4%E5%9B%9E%E6%98%A5%E4%BA%86-%E4%B8%8A%E9%8A%80-%E5%A4%A7%E9%8A%803%E6%9C%88%E7%87%9F%E6%94%B6%E9%9D%9A-%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E5%91%A8%E6%BC%B22%E6%88%90-030128325.html",
